{"tid":1544860,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［跪求增肥方法］呢三個月原來我瘦咗10kg","createTime":"2019-09-05T16:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T17:41:24.000Z","uid":76347,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"a828d66e793759a73c839f7d889fa5c010dc056f","tid":1544860,"uid":76347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:52:50.000Z","msg":"偏瘦底，但bmi仲算正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢場夢開始左之後，我辭左份工<br />\n為既係每一次既夢，我都可以發得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我留意到自己食越黎越少野，無時無刻都Mon post唔想miss咗任何一個資訊<br />\n叫左碟飯食一半已經無胃口<br />\n<br />\n朋友見到我，話我又瘦咗<br />\n本身無為意，心諗我不嬲瘦開架啦<br />\n但今晚我磅一磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得返47kg...<br />\n我本來已經係食整都唔肥果啲，一路都keep住55kg 左右<br />\n咁樣瘦左落去，我好驚我肥唔返<br />\n有冇巴絲可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f60d555646b7e1ab3eab850105073c70056449","tid":1544860,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:53:47.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"853e20fb2554e873051132a703dc6863a68f4de0","tid":1544860,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:56:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"775a438490ddd66a1a961dd894aa3084dd798a6a","tid":1544860,"uid":53915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:57:41.000Z","msg":"瘦咁多有機會係有病 建議check下"},{"pid":"67178710082a328b844cf48d27dc9f56a7023dee","tid":1544860,"uid":82940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:58:50.000Z","msg":"小食多餐<br />\n早起身食個大早餐 再去炒下散<br />\n咁11，12就餓又食<br />\n4點再食<br />\n8點再食<br />\n加宵夜<br />\n<br />\n我都係瘦撚<br />\n之前55 兩個月內宜家62"},{"pid":"001f9df6397288c01a5fc13add80c71db58a4fff","tid":1544860,"uid":291619,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:59:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa399202ff6da04182f40f10b96f650d3730a213","tid":1544860,"uid":76347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"67178710082a328b844cf48d27dc9f56a7023dee","tid":1544860,"uid":82940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:58:50.000Z","msg":"小食多餐<br />\n早起身食個大早餐 再去炒下散<br />\n咁11，12就餓又食<br />\n4點再食<br />\n8點再食<br />\n加宵夜<br />\n<br />\n我都係瘦撚<br />\n之前55 兩個月內宜家62"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:04:37.000Z","msg":"絲打朝早果餐係食啲咩 點大早餐法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9b39ce1ca73d4b88425b62a487e5ce66a804d0","tid":1544860,"uid":76347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"775a438490ddd66a1a961dd894aa3084dd798a6a","tid":1544860,"uid":53915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:57:41.000Z","msg":"瘦咁多有機會係有病 建議check下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"