我，話我又瘦咗<br />\n本身無為意，心諗我不嬲瘦開架啦<br />\n但今晚我磅一磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得返47kg...<br />\n我本來已經係食整都唔肥果啲，一路都keep住55kg 左右<br />\n咁樣瘦左落去，我好驚我肥唔返<br />\n有冇巴絲可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T19:33:21.000Z","msg":"我都係！平時食得哂一碟飯，而家食幾口就無胃口<br />\n而家輕左3. 幾kg"},{"pid":"2e21675b3ae945a929c53e24dfe69b7dc869aea5","tid":1544860,"uid":266569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c50b734bcba9a294fc02b590cbdfda59040d403","tid":1544860,"uid":76347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a5b2f3790ca1c5a52164ed665c5db3cfa9646e4","tid":1544860,"uid":126947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T19:10:22.000Z","msg":"我都係 越食越少 半夜會紮醒<br />\n呢幾日一訓個腦就係831"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T19:12:45.000Z","msg":"我未天光都唔會想訓 唉<br />\n跟住一起身就兩三點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T19:35:24.000Z","msg":"我都係"},{"pid":"6ac4d4f131445114138959af43550db8569c612f","tid":1544860,"uid":76347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a63088e250971e9a0da3a1683f1501bd1b366749","tid":1544860,"uid":266569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a828d66e793759a73c839f7d889fa5c010dc056f","tid":1544860,"uid":76347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:52:50.000Z","msg":"偏瘦底，但bmi仲算正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢場夢開始左之後，我辭左份工<br />\n為既係每一次既夢，我都可以發得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我留意到自己食越黎越少野，無時無刻都Mon post唔想miss咗任何一個資訊<br />\n叫左碟飯食一半已經無胃口<br />\n<br />\n朋友見到我，話我又瘦咗<br />\n本身無為意，心諗我不嬲瘦開架啦<br />\n但今晚我磅一磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得返47kg...<br />\n我本來已經係食整都唔肥果啲，一路都keep住55kg 左右<br />\n咁樣瘦左落去，我好驚我肥唔返<br />\n有冇巴絲可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T19:33:21.000Z","msg":"我都係！平時食得哂一碟飯，而家食幾口就無胃口<br />\n而家輕左3. 幾kg"},"citedBy":1,"repl